data.description: So many possibilities & upside potential, if you add some finishing touches! 1800+ sq ft, 3 BR (poss. 4th BR in lower level), 2 BA ranch home with an attached 2-car garage, a 14' x 22' in-ground pool, & a separate 22' x 22' building that could be finished ( could be additional sq ft) to be a pool house, a man cave, or she shed, work shop, or even a finished apartment (does have a 1/2 BA). Home is located on dead-end, quiet, oversized 0.4-acre cul-de-sac lot. The seller has made some improvements, including a new garage door, a new HVAC system, windows, an updated bathroom on the first floor, new stainless steel appliances, a new pump/filter for the pool, & more. Extras include a full walk-up basement, a huge pool deck, & more. Att Agents: See ATA remarks & offering instructions document.
